title: Bill Maher endorses Bernie Sanders, 'I want to see you be president'
text: Just days after the first Democratic debate and most voters are locked on Hillary Clinton and Bernie Sanders. While most media pundits declared Clinton the winner, the overwhelming consensus among liberal voters on social media was that Sanders was victorious. youtube.com
